# Tailwind CSS v4 Standards

This project uses Tailwind CSS v4. Always use the modern canonical utility classes to avoid IDE warnings and ensure future compatibility.

## Canonical Utility Renames

| Legacy Class (v3) | Canonical Class (v4) |
| :--- | :--- |
| `bg-gradient-to-*` | `bg-linear-to-*` |
| `break-words` | `wrap-break-word` |

### Examples

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
<div className="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 break-words">...</div>

// ✅ GOOD
<div className="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 wrap-break-word">...</div>
```

